869
00:54:10,093 --> 00:54:11,788
(WHIRRING)

870
00:54:58,408 --> 00:55:00,273
(GRUNTS)

871
00:55:00,344 --> 00:55:01,743
YBARRA: Hey! Stop!

872
00:55:02,846 --> 00:55:06,111
(GRUNTING)
Stop! Stop it! Stop it!

873
00:55:06,183 --> 00:55:09,243
Stop it! Stop it or I'll push
