939
00:58:27,350 --> 00:58:29,250
Christine.
Christine Collins.

940
00:58:31,288 --> 00:58:33,483
Now, finish it all. I know
it's hard, but you gotta try.

941
00:58:33,557 --> 00:58:34,854
WOMAN: Oh, boy.

